vice` 日志关键字：`\"Exception in thread\"`, `\"Injected error\"`, `\"caught ThrowException\"`, `\"AdService-getRandomAds-exception\"`.\n   - 日志还指出多次 Java 语言层面的错误和规则触发，如：`\"Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"`。\n\n### Common Fault Analysis\n- **Component**: `adservice`\n- **Detected Log Keys**: `rpc error`, `Unknown`, `Injected error`, `failed to retrieve ads`\n- **Hypotheses**:\n  1. **AdService Component Failure**:\n     - **Reason**: `adservice` 服务正在处理广告检索请求时发生了多个 Java 异常，这可能导致 `frontend` 无法正常检索广告，从而频繁报告广告检索失败错误。\n     - **Evidence**: 日志中频繁出现的 `AdService-getRandomAds-exception` 和 Java 栈帧异常表明问题集中在广告服务上。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"rpc error\", \"Unknown\", \"Injected error\", \"failed to retrieve ads\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service experiencing multiple Java-based exceptions during handling of getRandomAds requests, affecting ad retrieval.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService-getRandomAds-exception repeatedly logged with Java exceptions in adservice logs.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n根据已识别的日志信息，\"frontend\" 的广告请求失败是因为 \"adservice\" 的问题导致，这可能涉及到 \"adservice\" 的服务异常或内部实现故障。需进一步调查 \"adservice\" 的部署配置和代码实现以确认并修复根本问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据从2025-06-08T18:10:05Z到2025-06-08T18:29:05Z期间收集的指标数据，我们识别出以下显著的异常调用链：\n\n### Detected Metric Keys\n1. `node_memory_usage_rate`\n2. `pod_cpu_usage`\n3. `rrt_max`\n4. `client_error_ratio`\n5. `error_ratio`\n6. `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`\n7. `rrt`\n\n### Hypotheses\n\n#### Hypothesis 1\n- **Component**: `aiops-k8s-03` (Node)\n- **Reason**: The `node_memory_usage_rate` increased notably from 33.2% to 35.01%, indicating potential memory pressure on this node.\n- **Evidence**: Median change ratio was 0.0531, and p99 change ratio was 0.5488.\n\n#### Hypothesis 2\n- **Component**: `adservice-0` (Pod on aiops-k8s-03)\n- **Reason**: There was a spike in `pod_cpu_usage` from 0.01 during normal to 0.08, indicating increased load or activity.\n- **Evidence**: Median change ratio was 0.0, p99 change ratio was 1.5736.\n\n#### Hypothesis 3\n- **Component**: `emailservice-0` (Service)\n- **Reason**: `rrt_max` spiked significantly from 11602.12 to 58123.56, implying degraded performance that could affect user interactions.\n- **Evidence**: Median change ratio was 0.0339, p99 change ratio was 1.3344.\n\n#### Hypothesis 4\n- **Component**: `redis-cart-0` (Pod on aiops-k8s-08)\n- **Reason**: Observed `pod_cpu_usage` exhibited unusual activity patterns during the fault period.\n- **Evidence**: Median change ratio was 0.0, p99 change ratio was 0.6557.\n\n### Output JSON\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"rrt\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate increased from 33.2% to 35.01%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median change ratio: 0.0531, p99 change ratio: 0.5488\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Spiked pod_cpu_usage from 0.01 to 0.08\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median change ratio: 0.0, p99 change ratio: 1.5736\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max spiked from 11602.12 to 58123.56\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median change ratio: 0.0339, p99 change ratio: 1.3344\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Unusual pod_cpu_usage activity observed\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median change ratio: 0.0, p99 change ratio: 0.6557\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n``` \n\n请求进一步查看这些组件以验证问题，并采取适当的行动以解决故障。"}
